{
  "stem": "26142.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I forgot to mention that the commander of the Hungarian garrison that was the commander in Torun-- already they were in there for months-- he was a colonel, that was the highest ranking officer there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He took two rooms out of our house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he lived in our-- in our house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I should-- I should mention, he happened to be friendly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We gave him those-- those two rooms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And across the street from our house was the building of the Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That's where they had their headquarters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And you know, in the summertime, the windows were open in our house and the windows were open at school.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we could hear this-- this commander talking to the officers, Hungarian officers, that getting prepared because we are going to be attacking the Soviet Union and pep talks to the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Of course, I didn't understand a word of Hungarian, but my oldest brother that spoke Hungarian was in the house.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And-- and he-- he would explain what-- we overheard what they were saying.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Anyway, this-- this commander, that-- that colonel, came one day and told my father, and he said, it was-- it was in more less in a friendly, secretive mood, he wants to do us a favor.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he said, it would be advisable if you would move away from here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Move 20, 30, 40 kilometer-- kilometers down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because this is-- this is a war zone, a war zone here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We didn't know what he meant, if he wants to take us-- take away the house from us there because he-- he needs it or he is really trying to do us a favor.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Anyway, the-- the-- the movement, it was restricted because of all the military that were there.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
